[10/06/2017 20:51:11] <font color="#00ff00">Joe, Kenny.</font>
[10/06/2017 20:51:13] <font color="#00ff00">Adivina.</font>
[10/06/2017 20:51:15] <font color="#00ff00">Lena ha vuelto a su antigua casa.</font>
